dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line)  Winnebago County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Winnebago County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Winnebago_Hydro_2014.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Winnebago_HydroLine_2014' and 'Winnebago_HydroPoly_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
